snippet.title: neros77
snippet.description:
The Neros77 Channel specialises in music videos for synthwave and outrun electro synth and found footage from the 80s and 90s. If you have any requests please contact me here: sorenbrogger@ipaint.dk, my soundcloud or Facebook site.

Please support my Patreon site: 
https://www.patreon.com/neros77?fan_landing=true
